        <para>South Asian convergence</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Whether through unidirectional (Emeneau) or
            multi-directional (Hock) influence</para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Languages belong to many different families</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
